{"tid":1334673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人類成功登月50年","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:57:52.000Z","uid":24073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4fff15ba901731704bf97146b1cd65b5348a8de","tid":1334673,"uid":24073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"今日（7月20日）就係人類成功登月既50年<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?source=doodle-ntp&amp;v=uzbquKCqEQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsource%3Ddoodle-ntp%26v%3DuzbquKCqEQY&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=e61583e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?source=doodle-ntp&amp;v=uzbquKCqEQY</a><br />\n今日就係人類成功登月既50年<br />\n【明報專訊】「這是我的一小步，人類的一大步。」1969年7月20日，美國太空人岩士唐（Neil Armstrong）扶着梯子離開登月艙「鷹」號，將左腳踏在月球表面後說出這句名言，成為世上首個在月球留下足迹的人。"},{"pid":"94d73844b9b7d3f73cc5c43c710bec611e9a8827","tid":1334673,"uid":30163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7ad21d20ad4cdb23d43913cf0ff4f7100cf4863","tid":1334673,"uid":24073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2Gpune.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2Gpune.jpg&h=5192c399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《721&bull;不散》<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散唔係一句口號。<br />\n<br />\n從6.9到今日，民主之路仲有好長嘅一段，要大家一齊去行。<br />\n<br />\n當大家攰嘅時候，不妨回頭望下，你會發覺，我哋一直都喺度。<br />\n<br />\n7.21 維園見"}]}